Stunning Upgrades I Large Corner Plot

Brand new furnished 5-Bedroom Villa in Victory Heights located on a large corner plot – Modern Luxury Redefined

BlackBrick exclusively presents this exceptional 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom villa in the prestigious Victory Heights community. With a built-up area of 4,802 sq. ft. on a 7,100 sq. ft. plot, this residence seamlessly blends timeless elegance with contemporary design.

Key Features:
Spacious Living: Five luxurious bedrooms, including three with en-suite bathrooms.

Modern Upgrades: Newly renovated bathrooms featuring stylish RAK tiles and sleek black fittings.

Gourmet Kitchen: Redesigned to maximize storage space, elegant island, complemented by a separate laundry area and walk-in pantry.

Smart Home Features: Equipped with a new AC system controlled by Nest thermostats, smart lighting, and Ring doorbell.

Elegant Interiors: Herringbone LVT flooring, carpeted bedrooms, and high ceilings throughout.

Outdoor Oasis: A tranquil garden with a tiled pool, large pergola with fan, barbecue area, wine fridge, and lush greenery.

Additional Amenities: New front door, new water heaters, freshly painted interior and exterior, secure compound with electric garage doors.

Community Highlights:
Victory Heights offers lush golf course views and a luxurious lifestyle. Residents enjoy proximity to world-class golf courses, leisure facilities, and the largest park in the community.

This brand-new villa is ready for immediate occupancy.

Don't miss the opportunity to own this exquisite villa that epitomizes luxury living in Victory Heights.
